data.value: SELECT D.IdPrecio, D.FechaFin, D.Precio, P.Unidad, P.Descripcion, P.DescPres, Concepto.Concepto FROM PrecioDet AS D INNER JOIN (SELECT IdPrecio, MAX(FechaFin) AS FechaFin FROM PrecioDet AS a GROUP BY IdPrecio) AS D2 ON D.IdPrecio = D2.IdPrecio AND D.FechaFin = D2.FechaFin LEFT OUTER JOIN Precio AS P ON D.IdPrecio = P.IdPrecio LEFT OUTER JOIN Concepto ON P.IdConcepto = Concepto.IdConcepto WHERE (D.Precio IS NOT NULL) ORDER BY D.IdPrecio
